<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2014-08-21</DATELINE><TITLE>Food Safety: Emerging Pathogens</TITLE><BODY>This article presents information related to emerging pathogens that are foodborne or have the potential to be foodborne including bacteria, viruses, and parasites. The phenotypic characteristics of these pathogens, their epidemiology, prevalence in foods, and transmission routes to humans as well as means for their control are also discussed.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>